      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2020-09-29</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2020-12-08T15:47:56Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Protecting National Security in Financial Investments Act </b></p> <p>This bill requires the Securities and Exchange Commission to determine whether issuers of securities must disclose investments in certain persons reasonably believed to be involved, or to pose a significant risk of being or becoming involved, in activities contrary to the national security or foreign policy interests of the United States. </p> <p>The Department of State must annually submit to Congress a list of Chinese entities associated with specified military activities. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
